<div style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: #333;">
  <h2 style="color: #4CAF50;">New Login Notification</h2>
  <p>Dear {{username}},</p>
  <p>We noticed a new login to your account on
    {{loginDate}}
    from the following details:</p>

  <ul>
    <li><strong>Location:</strong> {{location}}</li>
    <li><strong>Device:</strong> {{device}}</li>
    <li><strong>Browser:</strong> {{browser}}</li>
    <li><strong>IP Address:</strong> {{ip}}</li>
    <li><strong>Operating System:</strong> {{os}}</li>
  </ul>

  <p>If this was you, no further action is needed. If you did not recognize this
    activity, please
    <a href="{{securityLink}}" style="color: #4CAF50;">secure your account</a>
    immediately.</p>

  <p>Best regards,<br />{{ companyName }} Team</p>

  <p style="font-size: 0.9em; color: #777;">For additional help, visit our
    support page or reply to this email.</p>
</div>